INSERT INTO `quiz_question` VALUES (139,'<p>Developed by Iwata et al. in 1994, this procedure assists with identifying the likely maintaining variables and is often used during an initial assessment to identify the likely &quot;cause&quot; of a problem behavior?</p>','2018-09-29 17:53:46','<p>A&nbsp;<strong>functional analysis</strong>&nbsp;is a type of functional assessment where consequences for problem behavior are manipulated in an&nbsp;<strong>alternating design</strong>&nbsp;to demonstrate which consequences are likely functional reinforcers for a given behavior.</p>

