INSERT INTO `pages_pages` VALUES (5,'Support ABA.Rocks!','<h2><span style="font-family:Verdana,Geneva,sans-serif"><strong>Three Ways to Show Some Love!</strong></span></h2>

<ul>
	<li><span style="font-size:16px"><span style="font-family:Verdana,Geneva,sans-serif"><a href="https://www.gofundme.com/support-abarocks">GoFundMe.com/Support-ABARocks</a></span></span></li>
	<li><span style="font-size:16px"><span style="font-family:Verdana,Geneva,sans-serif"><a href="https://www.patreon.com/abarocks">Patreon.com/ABARocks</a></span></span></li>
	<li><span style="font-size:16px"><span style="font-family:Verdana,Geneva,sans-serif"><a href="https://aba.rocks/coffee/">Buy Me a Coffee</a><em> (1-time donation of any amount)</em></span></span></li>
</ul>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<h2>My name is Alex, and I created this site, <a href="https://www.gofundme.com/support-abarocks"> </a><a class="txt1" href="http://www.aba.rocks," rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">www.aba.rocks,</a> to help people learn more about behavior analysis.</h2>

<p><br />
Behavior Analysis is a wonderful field that can do a whole lot of good to a whole lot of people. However, our science can be a bit confusing. There are easy concepts, but also a whole lot of difficult things to learn, especially for parents, newcomers to the field, and people from other sciences.</p>

<p>This can make it difficult for people to understand, let alone appreciate, which is a real shame - if we understood our own psychology better, we might be able to do really great things in the world. Reduce hatred and bigotry, improve the lives of the impoverished, create safer cities - all of these things could be realized through the application of the scientific method to the study of human behavior.&nbsp; It&#39;s my mission to spread the knowledge of Applied Behavior Analysis to as many as possible, and to make access to that knowledge free.<br />
<br />
<br />
<strong>If you want to support me financially, anything you can contribute is wonderful and amazing.</strong><br />
<br />
<strong>If you can&#39;t support financially, the best type of support you could provide anyone is to go out there and help people.</strong><br />
<br />
A big thank you, either way :)</p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p>Sincerely,</p>

<p style="margin-left:80px">Alex @ ABA.rocks</p>

