INSERT INTO `blog_post` VALUES (9,'Quizzes: Tweaks & Fixes','<h4><strong>Hello there!</strong></h4>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p>I&#39;ve been busy working on more practice quizzes as well as adding &quot;concept&quot; reviews to the site. One of the hold-ups is that I am beginning to require myself to cite research or sources before posting further content, as a quality assurance measure. It&#39;s been a lot of work, but what follows is a &quot;roadmap&quot; of sorts for the stuff I plan on creating over the coming weeks and months.</p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p>I also added a feature that makes the browser &quot;warn&quot; you if you attempt to click away during the quiz or accidentally hit the refresh key, to prevent you from losing your progress. You just have to hit &quot;OK&quot; to leave the quiz once you&#39;ve started it.</p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p>I&#39;ve also been focusing on creating a few mock quizzes that more closely follow the structure the BACB has created for the RBT Exam:</p>

